HEADWORD: Coriander
<hw>Co`ri*an"der</hw> <pr>(k?`r?-?n"d?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>coriandrum</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/<?/<?/<?/, <?/<?/<?/<?/, perh. fr.
